Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.91,Default,Dmir,0,0,0,,{TIME:224370,225913}I'm afraid so.{NOTE:おそらくは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:48.20,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:225913,228207}He's going to Gildegaran!?{NOTE:やつはギルデカランに!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.04,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:228207,231043}Let's go. We need to stop him.{NOTE:行こう。アンヴィスを止めに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:55.88,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:231711,235882}The emergency meeting to defend against an Elder Dragon is hereby opened!{NOTE:これより古龍防衛対策会議を開く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:58.92,Default,Guild Master,0,0,0,,{TIME:235882,238926}Thank you for coming here on such a short notice.{NOTE:皆の者よく集まってくれた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.76,Default,Guild Master,0,0,0,,{TIME:238926,240762}This is an emergency.{NOTE:事は急を要する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:05.80,Default,Guild Master,0,0,0,,{TIME:240762,245808}First of all, I'd like the head of the Royal Scriveners\Nto explain why you've been gathered here.{NOTE:まずはこの会議の発起人たる書士隊より概要を説明されたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.05,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:245808,247059}Sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:09.64,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:247059,249645}I'm Royal Scriveners' captain, Simone.{NOTE:私は書士隊隊長シモーヌ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:12.23,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:249645,252231}I'll be leading this meeting.{NOTE:この議事を仕切らせてもらう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:18.23,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:252231,258237}Fahali here reported sightings\Nof an Elder Dragon heading to Gildegaran.{NOTE:こちらにいるファマルよりギルデカランに向かう古龍の目撃情報がもたらされた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.23,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:258237,259238}An Elder Dragon?{NOTE:古龍？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.82,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:259238,260823}Yes.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.90,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:260823,262909}An Elder Dragon…{NOTE:鋼龍。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.66,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:262909,264660}Kushala Daora.{NOTE:クシャルダオラ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:31.62,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:266245,271626}According to the report, after bringing huge damage to Geo-Fulkright…{NOTE:報告によるとフルクライトジオに甚大な被害をもたらした後…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:35.54,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:271626,275546}…it's getting close to bring upon a disaster here in Gildegaran.{NOTE:…このギルデカランに災厄をもたらさんと接近している。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.38,Default,Knight A,0,0,0,,{TIME:275546,277381}Kushala Daora?{NOTE:クシャルダオラだと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:40.80,Default,Knight B,0,0,0,,{TIME:277381,280802}Are you certain it's headed to Gildegaran?{NOTE:このギルデカランに向かっているというのは本当なのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:43.22,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:280802,283221}I saw it with my own eyes.{NOTE:私はこの目で見た。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.84,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:283221,286849}It was heading straight here.{NOTE:やつは真っすぐにここに向かっているようだった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:52.81,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:286849,292814}To support Fahali's testimony, us Scriveners also dispatched our observation troops.{NOTE:ファマルの証言を裏付けるようにわれわれ書士隊が派遣している古龍観測隊からも…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.94,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:292814,294941}We received similar reports.{NOTE:…同様の報告が届いている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:58.73,Default,Knight A,0,0,0,,{TIME:294941,298736}However, an Elder Dragon is still a wild creature.{NOTE:しかし古龍とはいえ野生の生き物だぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.82,Default,Knight A,0,0,0,,{TIME:298736,301823}Why would it head from town to town?{NOTE:街から街へと真っすぐ来るものなのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:06.74,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:301823,306744}Certainly, the attack of the Elder Dragon has been regarded as a natural disaster until now.{NOTE:確かにこれまで古龍の襲来は天災とされてきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:11.62,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:306744,311624}However, it can be said that the situation is somewhat different this time.{NOTE:しかしながら今回はいささか状況が異なると言っていい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.29,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:311624,313292}This is human action.{NOTE:これは人災だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.16,Default,Knight B,0,0,0,,{TIME:314043,315169}Human action?!{NOTE:人災!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.63,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:315169,318631}This Kushala Daora isn't just a Monster.{NOTE:このクシャルダオラはただのモンスターではない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.88,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:318631,319882}It's a Monstie.{NOTE:オトモンなのだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.13,Default,Knight B,0,0,0,,{TIME:319882,322134}A Monstie, as in a Rider's?{NOTE:オトモンって…ライダーのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.21,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:322134,323219}Yes.{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:28.43,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:323219,328432}In other words, it's going to Gildegaran by its Rider's will.{NOTE:つまりライダーの意思によってこのギルデカランに向かっているということになる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:32.56,Default,Knight A,0,0,0,,{TIME:328432,332562}An Elder Dragon as a Monstie?\NIs that even possible?{NOTE:古龍をオトモンにだって!?そんなことが可能なのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.52,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:332562,333521}It is.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:39.65,Default,Simone,1,1,0,,{TIME:333520,339652}It seems that an Ebon Rider called Anvis is manipulating Kushala Daora through a forbidden technique.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズのアンヴィスという者が禁忌の秘術によってクシャルダオラを操っているらしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:47.28,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:341737,347285}If Kushala Daora is going here from Geo-Fulkright with the shortest distance…{NOTE:クシャルダオラがフルクライトジオから最短距離でここに向かっているというのならば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.99,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:347285,348995}We don't have much time.{NOTE:時間はあまりない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.33,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:348995,351330}We need to prepare countermeasures as soon as possible.{NOTE:早急に対策を立てなくては。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.41,Default,Knight A,0,0,0,,{TIME:351330,353416}Don't worry.{NOTE:心配はいらない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.25,Default,Knight A,0,0,0,,{TIME:353416,356252}Gildegaran is protected by a solid wall.{NOTE:ギルデカランは堅固な城壁で守られている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.54,Default,Knight B,0,0,0,,{TIME:356252,357545}Yes.{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:01.84,Default,Knight B,0,0,0,,{TIME:357545,361841}Gildegaran can withstand any Monster assault,\Nbe it Kushala Daora or whatnot.{NOTE:ギルデカランならばクシャルダオラだろうがオトモンだろうが大丈夫だろうさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.09,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:361841,363092}Yeah!{NOTE:そうだな！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.09,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:363092,365094}If we stay here, we'll be okay.{NOTE:ここにいれば。俺たちも大丈夫だろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.26,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:365094,366262}We can use the wall as a shield…{NOTE:城壁を盾にして…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.05,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:366262,369056}You seem to be forgetting one thing.{NOTE:お前ら一つ勘違いしてるみたいだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:14.64,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:370308,374645}The walls of Gildegaran do not protect the Hunters.{NOTE:このギルデカランの城壁はハンターを守るもんじゃねえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:17.06,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:374645,377064}It's there to protect the civilians inside.{NOTE:中の民間人を守るためのもんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.27,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:377815,379275}Then what should we do?{NOTE:じゃあ俺たちはどうすれば…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.61,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:379275,380610}Escape while there's still time?{NOTE:今のうちに逃げた方が。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:22.77,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:380610,382778}Do we stand any chance against it?{NOTE:対抗できるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.44,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:382778,384447}Don't worry.{NOTE:でも心配すんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.07,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:384447,386073}Look around.{NOTE:見てみろよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:30.20,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:386073,390202}We have the best Hunters around here in Gildegaran.{NOTE:このｷﾞﾙﾃﾞｶﾗﾝには手だれのﾊﾝﾀｰがごまんといる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:33.24,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:390202,393247}Kushala Daora won't lay a claw on anyone.{NOTE:クシャルダオラなんかに後れはとらねえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.12,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:393247,394123}Don't you think?{NOTE:そうだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.41,Default,Knight B,0,0,0,,{TIME:394123,395416}Y-Yeah.{NOTE:お…おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.25,Default,Knight A,0,0,0,,{TIME:395416,397251}Let's hunt!{NOTE:狩ってやろうぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.33,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:397251,399337}Yeah!{NOTE:おおー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.21,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:399503,400212}Well said.{NOTE:うむ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:43.21,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:400212,403215}We'll meet with Kushala Daora outside the fortress.{NOTE:クシャルダオラは城の外で迎え撃つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.05,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:403215,405051}– Please wait.\N– Hm?{NOTE:—お待ちください！\\N—ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.30,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:405051,407303}Please think this through.{NOTE:少し冷静になってもらいたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.89,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:407303,410890}There are many Hunters here in Gildegaran indeed.{NOTE:確かにギルデカランには手だれのハンターが多くいる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:57.14,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:410890,417146}However, there are few Hunters who have dealt with Kushala Daora before.{NOTE:しかしながらここにいるハンターでもｸｼｬﾙﾀﾞｵﾗと相まみえたことのある者はほとんどいないはず。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:04.27,Default,Guild Master,0,0,0,,{TIME:420608,424278}As Simone says, few of us may have the experience.{NOTE:シモーヌが言うとおり経験はないかもしれん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:09.32,Default,Guild Master,0,0,0,,{TIME:424278,429325}But we have accumulated vast knowledge in the history of hunting.{NOTE:じゃがわれらには狩りの歴史の中で培った多くの知識がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:09.99,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:429325,429992}{NOTE:あっ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:13.49,Default,Guild Master,0,0,0,,{TIME:431285,433496}You know I'm right, Simone.{NOTE:そうじゃろう？シモーヌ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:15.99,Default,Guild Master,0,0,0,,{TIME:434372,435998}{NOTE:うむ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.75,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:436791,438751}You're certainly right.{NOTE:確かにそうです…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:23.63,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:438751,443631}The Scriveners have collected a lot of information on Kushala Daora.{NOTE:書士隊にはｸｼｬﾙﾀﾞｵﾗに関する情報の蓄積があります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:28.21,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:443631,448219}Tell us more about the information that you have gathered.{NOTE:その書士隊が持ってるクシャルダオラに関する情報を教えてくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.80,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:448219,449804}Very well.{NOTE:分かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.01,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:449804,453015}Let's clarify all the information of the squadron.{NOTE:書士隊の持つ全ての情報を明かそう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:39.81,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:454767,459814}Originally, it was impossible to tie the Elder Dragons to any specific ecosystem.{NOTE:そもそも古龍種というのは特定の生態系に分類すらできない…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.90,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:459814,462900}These unknown Monsters were named so mainly for convenience.{NOTE:…未知なるモンスターを便宜上そう呼んでいるだけで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:48.03,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:462900,468030}One thing we've been sure: we couldn't find out anything about their origins.{NOTE:…その生態についてはほとんど解明されていないのが実情だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:52.61,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:468030,472618}Still, through the accumulated experience of many Hunters…{NOTE:それでも多くのハンターが狩りを通じて得た経験によって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:56.95,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:472618,476956}…we've gained some information related to how to fight them.{NOTE:…その戦い方に関する情報が多くもたらされている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:08:01.58,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:476956,481585}Such as that Kushala Daora always appears within a storm.{NOTE:クシャルダオラは嵐と共に現れる…とかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.08,Default,Felyne,0,0,0,,{TIME:482837,484088}{NOTE:ニャ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:11.30,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:484964,491303}Or that Kushala Daora sometimes wraps itself with a tornado as a form of protection.{NOTE:クシャルダオラは風を操り自らを包むように竜巻をまとうこともあるという。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:28.44,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:500104,508446}Unlike many dragons, it has strong front and back legs apart from its strong wings.{NOTE:その姿は多くの飛竜と異なり翼とは別に強靱な前脚と後ろ脚が存在する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:34.20,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:508446,514201}In addition, because Kushala Daora is entirely covered with steel-like scales and crust shells…{NOTE:さらにクシャルダオラは全身が鋼鉄のうろこや甲殻に覆われていることから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:37.12,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:514201,517121}…the body is so strong that it is called a Steel Dragon.{NOTE:…鋼龍と呼ばれるほどその体は強固だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:46.58,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:522293,526589}Finally, Kushala Daora's biggest weapon is…{NOTE:そしてクシャルダオラの最大の武器は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:50.63,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:526589,530634}…a Breath of a tremendous wind power that spits out of its mouth.{NOTE:…口から吐き出すすさまじい風圧を伴うブレスだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.72,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:537683,540728}According to Hunters' reports of past encounters…{NOTE:過去遭遇したハンターの報告によると…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:05.27,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:540728,545274}…it was said to be so strong that one couldn't move anywhere near it.{NOTE:…至近距離を通過しただけで動けなくなるほどの風圧であったという。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.73,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:545274,547735}I have also heard of it.{NOTE:それなら俺も聞いたことがある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.82,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:547735,549820}It's called Dragon Wind Pressure.{NOTE:龍風圧というやつだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:14.28,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:549820,554283}It's said it makes it difficult just to approach it.{NOTE:それがあるかぎり近づくことすら困難だといわれている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:20.53,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:554283,560539}In other words, one can't attack unless\Nthe Dragon Wind Pressure is taken care of…{NOTE:つまりその龍風圧ってのを何とかしないと攻撃が通らないということか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:25.33,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:560539,565336}In any case, every Monster can be defeated, even an Elder Dragon.{NOTE:だが古龍だろうと何だろうと倒せないモンスターはいない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.75,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:565336,568756}Every living thing has a weakness.{NOTE:生き物であるかぎりどこかに弱点はあるはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.50,Default,Guild Master,0,0,0,,{TIME:569340,571509}Hmm…{NOTE:う～ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:35.17,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:572218,575179}Does it, now?{NOTE:あるのか？弱点が。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:35.84,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:575179,575846}Yes.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:41.01,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:577056,581018}Kushala Daora's weak point…{NOTE:クシャルダオラの弱点…それが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.02,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:581018,583020}…are its horns.{NOTE:この角と思われる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.10,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:583020,584105}Horns?{NOTE:角？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:49.65,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:584105,589652}Now that you mention it, I've heard something similar from a Hunter that fought with Kushala Daora before.{NOTE:確かに昔クシャルダオラと戦ったというハンターに聞いたことがある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.94,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:589652,592947}He said the storm ceases when you break its horns.{NOTE:角を折ったら嵐がやんだと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:55.86,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:592947,595866}I thought it was just a folk story, though.{NOTE:てっきりホラ話と思っていたが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:10:04.95,Default,Simone,1,1,0,,{TIME:595866,604959}According to our research, Kushala Daora's ability to control the wind involves the horns on the back of its head.{NOTE:クシャルダオラの風をまとう能力にはこの頭部後方に向かって生えた角が関係しているという研究報告が上がってきている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:12.17,Default,Simone,1,1,0,,{TIME:604959,612174}Therefore I think it's safe to say that if one broke its horns, it couldn't use its Dragon Wind Pressure anymore.{NOTE:故に角を破壊された個体は龍風圧をまとうことができなくなると思われる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.42,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:612174,615427}In other words, we should aim for the horns.{NOTE:要するに角をへし折れってことか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:21.55,Default,Knight A,0,0,0,,{TIME:615427,621559}But as long as that Dragon Wind Pressure is there, we can't get even close to the horns.{NOTE:だけどその龍風圧があるかぎり角を折るところまで近づけないんじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.31,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:621559,623310}Yeah…{NOTE:うむ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.72,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:623310,624728}Can I have a moment?{NOTE:ちょっといいか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.81,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:624728,625813}Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:29.90,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:625813,629900}The Hunter who told me about his fight with Kushala Daora said this:{NOTE:ｸｼｬﾙﾀﾞｵﾗとの戦いを話してくれたハンターがこうも言っていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:34.69,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:631152,634697}"You can suppress the wind by attacking with poison."{NOTE:毒による攻撃で風を抑えられると。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.15,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:634697,636157}I see.{NOTE:なるほど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:40.45,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:636157,640452}If we poison it, its control over wind will worsen…{NOTE:毒によって体の機能が低下すればあるいは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.70,Default,Knight A,0,0,0,,{TIME:640452,641704}Poison, huh?{NOTE:毒か。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:47.54,Default,Knight B,0,0,0,,{TIME:641704,647543}Then you can count on us Gunners.\NWe'll shoot poison bombs at it.{NOTE:それならガンナーによる毒弾の射撃攻撃なら効果が期待できるぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.79,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:647543,649795}Then the course of action has been decided.{NOTE:となれば方針は決まった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:53.09,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:649795,653090}The only thing's left is to make detailed strategy.{NOTE:あとは具体的な作戦立案をするだけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.42,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:653090,654425}Yes sir.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:57.97,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:654425,657970}We invite all the Hunters in Gildegaran to join us.{NOTE:ギルデカランにいるハンター全員に招集をかけます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.26,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:657970,660264}Is that okay, Guild Master?{NOTE:よろしいですね？ギルドマスター。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.30,Default,Guild Master,0,0,0,,{TIME:660264,661307}Yes.{NOTE:うむ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.05,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:663392,664059}Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.48,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:665352,668480}What's wrong? Is there anything more you're worried about?{NOTE:どうした？まだ何か不安があるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:11.40,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:668480,671400}Yes, just one thing.{NOTE:ああ。一つだけある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:14.57,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:671400,674570}I wouldn't be anxious if we were up against just a Kushala Daora.{NOTE:相手がただのｸｼｬﾙﾀﾞｵﾗならば問題はない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:17.57,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:674570,677573}But this time it's a Monstie.{NOTE:しかし今回の相手はオトモン。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.49,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:677573,679491}That's to say, a Rider.{NOTE:つまりライダーだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:22.41,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:679491,682411}We can't be sure what kind of attack to expect.{NOTE:どのような攻撃に出るか不確定だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.07,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:682411,684079}That's what I'm worried about.{NOTE:そこが不安なのだ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.99,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:684914,685998}I see.{NOTE:ふむ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:30.00,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:685998,690002}We have no experience of fighting Riders.{NOTE:われらにはライダーとの戦いの経験はないからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:33.00,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:690002,693005}I wish we had at least that bunch with us…{NOTE:せめてあいつらがいてくれればな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:36.42,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:693005,696425}Ah, you have a point.\NThey'd be of great use.{NOTE:あっ…確かに彼らがいれば。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.96,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:696425,697968}These guys, huh…{NOTE:やつらか…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.34,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:698802,700346}I'm sorry we're late!{NOTE:遅くなりました！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:44.51,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:700346,704516}We, the Riders of Hakum Village,\Nwould like to assist you on the battlefield as well.{NOTE:われわれハクム村のライダーも微力ながら戦陣に加えていただきたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.31,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:710856,712316}Oh? They're here.{NOTE:あっ来た。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.52,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:712316,714526}Huh? Is something wrong?{NOTE:えっ？な…何か問題でも？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.28,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:715861,718280}No, no! Everything's just perfect!{NOTE:いやいや問題などない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:01.65,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:718280,721659}Good to see you here! Hahaha!{NOTE:よく来てくれたなワハハハハ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:05.49,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:721659,725496}I know it's sudden, but please tell me about your Monsties' abilities.{NOTE:早速だが君たちのオトモンの戦力を教えてくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:08.12,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:725496,728123}Huh? Right now?{NOTE:えっ？いきなり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.58,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:728123,729583}R-Right away…{NOTE:あっはい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:13.33,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:731252,733337}I don't understand it very well, but…{NOTE:何だかよく分からないけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.88,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:733337,735881}…at any rate, we seem to have made it in time.{NOTE:とにかく間に合ったみたいだね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.13,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:735881,738133}Hey. Where's Lute?{NOTE:おいリュートはどうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.42,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:738133,740427}I can't see Cheval with you either.{NOTE:シュヴァルの姿も見えないが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:24.68,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:740427,744682}Yeah. What happened to the Riders who stopped the Black Blight?{NOTE:おう。あの黒の凶気を止めたライダーはどうしたんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:27.14,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:744682,747142}Figures. They're not here yet.{NOTE:やっぱりまだ来てないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:28.85,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:747142,748852}What do you mean?{NOTE:どういうことだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:31.14,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:748852,751146}It'll be fine!{NOTE:大丈夫っすよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.64,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:751146,753649}Lute will come for sure!{NOTE:リュート先輩なら来るっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:34.81,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:753649,754817}Nariki?{NOTE:ナリキ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:35.69,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:754817,755693}Uhm…{NOTE:うーん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:39.15,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:755693,759154}I don't know where Lute and Cheval are.{NOTE:リュート先輩たちがどこにいるかは分からないっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:42.03,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:759154,762032}But they'll definitely come, no matter what happens.{NOTE:でも何があっても必ず来るんすよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.99,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:762032,763993}They're just that kind of people.{NOTE:そういう人なんで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.41,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:763993,765411}{NOTE:へへっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.24,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:766954,769248}Lute's junior?{NOTE:リュートの後輩か。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.91,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:769248,771917}I agree. He'll come here for sure.{NOTE:確かにあいつなら来るな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.21,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:771917,773210}There's no doubt about it.{NOTE:間違いなく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.79,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:773210,774795}Yeah!{NOTE:うっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:13:01.71,Default,Beats,1,1,0,,{TIME:774795,781719}All right then, now we'll discuss a strategy to hunt an Elder Dragon\Nand cooperation between Hunters and Riders.{NOTE:それではこれよりハンターとライダー共同で古龍に立ち向かう作戦立案を行う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.01,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:781719,784013}Yeah!{NOTE:おー！}
Comment: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:04.01,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:784013,784013}Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.97,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:784596,786974}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:08.01,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:786974,788017}Rathalos!{NOTE:リオレウス！}
Comment: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:08.01,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:788016,788016}#Black screen
Comment: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:10.01,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:790019,790019}$Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.02,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:794023,794023}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:26.20,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:802448,806201}After we cross Trese Desert, it's Gildegaran.{NOTE:このクバ砂漠を越えればギルデカランだっていうのに｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.62,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:806201,808620}We pushed it crossing the ocean.{NOTE:無理して海を越えてきたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.41,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:808620,811415}We have to rest for a while.{NOTE:一度翼を休めないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:33.83,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:811415,813834}Otherwise we won't be able to fight Anvis.{NOTE:アンヴィスと戦うこともできなくなってしまうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:38.13,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:815544,818130}I know that.{NOTE:分かってるけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:41.34,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:818130,821342}It'd be great if there was a way to get there faster…{NOTE:もっと速く飛べる方法があればいいのですが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.64,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:829224,831643}We have to eat, too.{NOTE:私たちも食べないと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.72,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:831643,832728}Yep.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.97,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:832728,833979}Thanks.{NOTE:ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.15,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:839485,841153}You too, Brother.{NOTE:兄さんも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:02.23,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:841153,842237}Thanks.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.99,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:846742,847993}Can I talk to you for a bit?{NOTE:ちょっといいか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.33,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:855292,857336}What did you want to talk about?{NOTE:何ですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.71,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:857336,859713}Turn around and fly back.{NOTE:お前はここで引き返せ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.21,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:859713,861215}Why would I do such thing?{NOTE:なぜそんなことを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.30,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:861215,863300}Your Kinship Stone…{NOTE:その絆石…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:27.05,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:863300,867054}Did you know that it's the Stone that Dad used to wear?{NOTE:それは父さんがつけていたものだということは知っているな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.51,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:867054,868514}Yes.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:31.18,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:868514,871183}I heard it.{NOTE:そう聞いています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.56,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:871183,873560}Dad kept always saying…{NOTE:父さんはいつも言ってた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:37.89,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:873560,877898}"You'll grow up to be a great Rider some day."{NOTE:お前は大人になったら自分のような立派なライダーになれと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.85,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:878941,880859}Really?{NOTE:父さんが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:43.65,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:880859,883654}Dad was kind.{NOTE:父さんは優しい人だった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:46.03,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:883654,886031}Too kind for his own good.{NOTE:ただ優しすぎたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:49.70,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:886031,889701}That's why men like Anvis could take advantage of him.{NOTE:だからアンヴィスのような男に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.87,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:889701,891870}You resemble Dad.{NOTE:お前は父さんに似ている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.91,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:891870,894915}That's why I don't want you to fight.{NOTE:だから戦いなど望んでいないはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.37,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:896959,898377}Avinia…{NOTE:アユリア…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.29,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:898377,901296}Please protect that Kinship Stone.{NOTE:その絆石を守ってくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:04.80,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:902631,904800}For Dad's sake.{NOTE:父さんの形見をな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.68,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:912141,914685}I'll go with you.{NOTE:私は行きます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:18.06,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:914685,918063}I was born to our family as a priest as well.{NOTE:私も神官だった父の子として生まれたんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.18,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:918063,919189}Avinia!{NOTE:アユリア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.07,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:925571,927072}I understand.{NOTE:分かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:32.28,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,{TIME:928574,932286}Dan's group should arrive in Gildegaran by now.{NOTE:今ごろダンたちがギルデカランに着いてるころじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.32,Default,Geezer A,0,0,0,,{TIME:932286,934329}Will things go well?{NOTE:大丈夫かのう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:36.16,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:934329,936165}There's no use in worrying.{NOTE:心配は無用じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:39.20,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:936165,939209}I'm sure they can handle the task we had given them.{NOTE:彼らならばきっと成し遂げてくれよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.46,Default,Geezer B,0,0,0,,{TIME:939209,942463}They all grew to be so strong.{NOTE:皆たくましく成長したからのう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.96,Default,Geezer B,0,0,0,,{TIME:942463,944965}They remind me of us in the old days.{NOTE:昔のわしらを見るようじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:48.46,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,{TIME:944965,948469}What do you know?\NThey have long surpassed us.{NOTE:な～にわしらよりも立派になったわい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:52.09,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:948469,952097}In every society, it's youth that pushes the world forward.{NOTE:いつの世も時代をつくるのは若者じゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.64,Default,Geezer B,0,0,0,,{TIME:952097,954641}But now the village is defenseless.{NOTE:おかげで村の守りがおらんがの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:58.85,Default,Gamigami,0,0,0,,{TIME:954641,958854}Pfft! I'll drive away any Monster that tries to get close!{NOTE:なーにモンスターが現れたらわしが追い払ってくれるわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.31,Default,Geezer A,0,0,0,,{TIME:958854,962316}Exactly! We're old but we're still Riders!{NOTE:そうじゃとも！年は取ってもライダーじゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:06.86,Default,Geezer B,0,0,0,,{TIME:962316,966862}Did you already forget how you had your butt handed to you the last time?{NOTE:そんなこと言ってお前。前も蹴散らされてたがな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:09.28,Default,Geezer A,0,0,0,,{TIME:966862,969281}You didn't need to say that.{NOTE:それを言ってくれるな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.66,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:970574,973660}Please protect them…{NOTE:彼らを守ってくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:14.82,Default,Geezer A,0,0,0,,{TIME:973660,974828}Vlau.{NOTE:ヴラウ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.37,Default,Fahali,0,0,0,,{TIME:978457,980375}Hurry up with that ballista!{NOTE:バリスタの設置急げ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.54,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:980959,982544}{\an8}Heave-ho!{NOTE:そーれ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.25,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:982544,984254}{\an8}Heave-ho!{NOTE:そーれ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.04,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:984254,986048}{\an8}Heave-ho!{NOTE:そーれ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.88,Default,Nole,0,0,0,,{TIME:986298,988884}Keep pulling! Aptonoth!{NOTE:引っ張れアプトノス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.59,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:989801,991595}This is spectacular.{NOTE:こりゃあ壮観だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:35.89,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:992930,995891}I've never seen a battlefield of this size.{NOTE:こんな規模の作戦見たことないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.43,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:996391,997434}Yeah.{NOTE:ええ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:39.72,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:997434,999728}It's truly in top form.{NOTE:まさに絶好調だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:41.60,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:999728,1001605}We're up against a Kushala Daora.{NOTE:相手はクシャルダオラ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.48,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001605,1004483}A Monstie, on top of that.{NOTE:しかもオトモンの迎撃戦。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.81,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004483,1006818}That alone might be not enough.{NOTE:この規模でも足りないかもしれん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:50.23,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006818,1010239}Ah, I feel nervous and my head is blank…{NOTE:ああ～緊張で頭真っ白っす…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.53,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010239,1011532}Hey, hey.{NOTE:おいおい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:55.41,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011532,1015410}Don't forget you have an important role.{NOTE:お前らは重要な役割を担ってるんだ。忘れるなよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:17:00.37,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015410,1020374}Thinking about it doesn't help.{NOTE:そんなこと言われても緊張っす…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.91,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020374,1021917}Captain Gentor.{NOTE:ゲントラス隊長。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:06.04,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021917,1026046}They're nervous. Could you explain them the strategy once more to calm them down?{NOTE:緊張している彼らに作戦をいま一度説明してもらえるか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.00,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026046,1027005}Sure.{NOTE:ああ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:10.46,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027004,1030467}I just adjusted the operation progress.{NOTE:ちょうど進行状況を整理していたところだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:15.05,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030467,1035055}The aim of the first stage is to stop the invasion of the Elder Dragon.{NOTE:第一段階の目的は古龍の侵攻を止めることだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:20.18,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035055,1040185}{\fad(0,500)}We deployed a squad of Gunlancers equipped with shields on Kushala Daora's invasion route.{NOTE:クシャルダオラ侵攻ルート上に盾を装備したガンランス隊を配備した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.18,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1040727,1042187}Shield Wall!{NOTE:盾の壁～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:23.77,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1042186,1043771}Yeah!{NOTE:おおー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:29.06,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044940,1049069}They won't be blown off so easily.{NOTE:彼らならばそうやすやすと吹き飛ばされたりはせんからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.32,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1049319,1052322}Keep calm and don't let go!{NOTE:お前ら慌ててぶっ放すなよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:35.07,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1052322,1055075}Attract the enemy and aim precisely!{NOTE:敵を引きつけ確実に当てろ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:36.70,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1055075,1056702}Yeah!{NOTE:おおー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.87,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057536,1060872}Then, once we manage to stop Kushala Daora's advance…{NOTE:そしてクシャルダオラの動きを止めたところで…}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.95,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060872,1063959}…a team of Heavy Bowgunners will carry out a poison bombardment.{NOTE:…ヘビィボウガン隊による毒弾砲撃。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:47.79,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063959,1067796}Can we have any assistance from the air?{NOTE:空を飛べるオトモンに上空から援護を頼めないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.13,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067796,1069131}I understand.{NOTE:なるほど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:52.59,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069130,1072593}You'd like to attack it from both ground and the sky.{NOTE:地上と上空からの挟み撃ちというわけですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.84,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072593,1073844}I see.{NOTE:分かりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:59.26,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073844,1079266}The wind will weaken from the poison bombardment.{NOTE:ガンナー隊によってクシャルダオラに毒が回れば風が弱まるはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:04.93,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079266,1084938}Then we can concentrate the simultaneous attacks of the ballista troops on the horns.{NOTE:そうなればバリスタ部隊の一斉攻撃を角に集中させて破壊できる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:08.90,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084938,1088900}Monsties who are capable of long range attacks will also participate.{NOTE:長距離攻撃が可能なオトモンも攻撃に参加します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.36,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088900,1090360}It's a good plan.{NOTE:いい案だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:15.57,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090360,1095574}I'd like to add smoke balls and poisonous smoke balls somewhere.{NOTE:もう一つけむり玉と毒けむり玉によるかく乱を予定している。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:19.11,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095574,1099119}Will these have any effect on an Elder Dragon?{NOTE:わなも効かない古龍に効果があるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:23.41,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099119,1103415}Well, it won't hurt for sure.\NIt was a suggestion from our reinforcements.{NOTE:援軍からの提案でなやってみる価値はある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.91,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103415,1104916}Reinforcements?{NOTE:援軍？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:27.79,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104916,1107793}Yeah. Seems like they've just arrived.{NOTE:ああちょうど到着したようだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.71,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110130,1111715}Ah! Them!?{NOTE:あっ！あいつらは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.30,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1113800,1116303}We're sorry we made you wait.{NOTE:皆さんお待たせしました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.22,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1116303,1118221}Meow! Meow! Meow!{NOTE:ニャイニャイニャー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:41.05,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118597,1121058}They're Felynes from Pawpad Place!{NOTE:ニクキュー村のアイルーたちだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.43,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121058,1122434}Felynes?{NOTE:アイルー？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.22,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122434,1124227}Hahaha!{NOTE:ハハハハハ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:47.02,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1124895,1127022}We'll lend you a paw in this battle.{NOTE:われわれも参戦します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:50.19,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1127022,1130192}When we heard about the crisis in Gildegaran, we rushed here to help.{NOTE:ｷﾞﾙﾃﾞｶﾗﾝの危機と聞いてはせ参じたニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.44,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1130192,1132444}I'm sure we'll be of help to you!{NOTE:きっと役に立ってみせるニャ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:56.32,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132444,1136323}I'm leaving the implementation of the strategies you suggested to you.{NOTE:諸君らが提案してくれた作戦の方は任せたぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.65,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1136322,1137658}You can count on us!{NOTE:任せるニャ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:59.53,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1137658,1139534}{NOTE:—ニャイニャイニャー！\\N—グッシャッシャー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:02.32,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1139534,1142329}We'll begin with our preparations right away!{NOTE:ではわれわれも準備に取り掛かるニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.70,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1142329,1143705}{NOTE:—ニャイニャイニャー！\\N—グッシャッシャー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.25,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144623,1147250}Once we break the horns, it's time for stage two.{NOTE:角が折れたら第２段階だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:13.79,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147250,1153799}We'll switch the ammo in ballista to restrain nets and we'll pin Kushala Daora to the ground.{NOTE:バリスタを拘束弾に切り替えクシャルダオラを地面に引きずり落とす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:17.01,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153799,1157010}Then we'll attack it from all sides.{NOTE:そうなれば一斉攻撃か。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.34,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157010,1159346}We'll lead the Riders' team.{NOTE:われらライダー隊も突撃します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.47,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1159346,1160472}{NOTE:—えっ。\\N—うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:21.80,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160472,1161807}Good.{NOTE:うむ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:28.93,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161807,1168939}Until Kushala Daora… no… Until Anvis collapses, I want you to keep attacking at full power.{NOTE:クシャルダオラが…いや…アンヴィスが倒れるまで攻撃の手を緩めるつもりはない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.31,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168939,1170315}What about you, Reverto?{NOTE:リヴェルトは？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.81,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170315,1172818}I was assigned to the commando unit.{NOTE:俺は遊撃隊を任されている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:35.07,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172818,1175070}We'll observe the situation and act accordingly.{NOTE:状況を見て戦うさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:39.32,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175070,1179324}I think Reverto will work best when we give him freedom.{NOTE:リヴェルトは自由に動いてもらった方がいいと思ってな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:40.95,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179324,1180951}Thanks.{NOTE:助かります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:45.78,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180951,1185789}As a leader of the commando unit,\NI'd like a little more firepower, though.{NOTE:ただ遊撃隊としてはもう少し火力が欲しいとこですけどね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.37,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185789,1187374}Don't be like that.{NOTE:そう言うな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.83,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187374,1190836}I can't cut you anything more.{NOTE:これでも割ける戦力は全て回しているんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:53.33,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190836,1193338}I know, but still…{NOTE:分かっちゃいますけどね…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.04,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193338,1194047}Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.88,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194047,1195882}Is something wrong, Spex?{NOTE:ピント？どうかしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.72,Default,Floof,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200470,1202723}What can you see?{NOTE:何が見えるんでしゅニャ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:06.60,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202723,1206601}Looks like something's approaching from Trese Desert.{NOTE:クバ砂漠方面から何かやって来るゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:09.39,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206601,1209396}Ah! Don't tell me it's Kushala Daora already?{NOTE:あっ…まさかクシャルダオラか!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.73,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1209396,1210731}{NOTE:あっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.56,Default,Simone,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211356,1213567}It's earlier than we calculated!{NOTE:計算よりも早い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:14.35,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213567,1214359}Ah!{NOTE:あっ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:15.81,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214359,1215819}Spit it out already!{NOTE:だから何だよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.28,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215819,1219281}It's not a Kushala Daora! It's a group of Hunters!{NOTE:クシャルダオラじゃなくたくさんのハンターゴロニャ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.24,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219281,1220240}Hunters?{NOTE:ハンター？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:23.86,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222576,1223869}They're…{NOTE:あれは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:28.45,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226121,1228456}Hunters from Albrachs Village!{NOTE:アルブラクス村のハンター！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.71,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229291,1231710}Thanks for coming here.{NOTE:お前たちよく来てくれたな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:38.00,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1231710,1238008}You Riders saved our Albrachs Village during the Black Blight crisis.{NOTE:黒の凶気のとき俺たちアルブラクス村のハンターはライダーに救われた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:41.01,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1238008,1241011}Time to return the favor!{NOTE:今度はその借りを俺たちが返す番だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.22,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:1241011,1243221}Yeah!{NOTE:おおー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:46.34,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243221,1246349}I'd all of your Hunters to join my commando unit.{NOTE:みんなには俺の遊撃隊に加わってもらいたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:47.35,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{TIME:1246349,1247350}Sure!{NOTE:ああ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:54.69,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251938,1254691}With your men I don't need to worry about our firepower anymore.{NOTE:これで心配だった火力も十分だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:55.65,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254691,1255650}Good.{NOTE:うむ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:59.94,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255649,1259946}Wave attacks of Hunters and Riders will give it a hard time.{NOTE:ハンターとライダーによる波状攻撃にも厚みが増した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:01.32,Default,Gentor,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259946,1261323}We can win!{NOTE:勝てるぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.74,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268955,1270749}Don't worry.{NOTE:心配するな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:12.50,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270749,1272501}Lute will come for sure.{NOTE:リュートは必ず来るさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:13.50,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272501,1273502}Yeah.{NOTE:うっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:18.04,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275337,1278048}Hey! Everyone!{NOTE:おーい！みんなー！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:21.63,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278048,1281635}Ah, that voice just now! It was Lute!{NOTE:あっ！今リュート先輩の声がしたっす！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:22.34,Default,Reverto,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281635,1282344}Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.34,0:21:24.05,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282344,1284053}Look up!{NOTE:上だよ上！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.97,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286014,1287974}Lute!{NOTE:リュート先輩！}
